{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/golf-code","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Golf Kod","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U golfu, svaka rupa ima <code>par</code>, sto predstavlja prosecan broj <code>strokes</code> (udaraca) koji se ocekuje da igrac napravi da ubaci lopticu u rupu. U zavisnosti od toga koliko su vasi <code>strokes</code> iznad ili ispod <code>par</code> vrednosti, koristi se razlicit naziv.</p>\n<p>Vasa funkcija prima argumente <code>par</code> i <code>strokes</code>. Vratite odgovarajuci string prema sledecoj tabeli koja navodi ishode po prioritetu, od vrha (najvisi prioritet) ka dnu (najnizi prioritet):</p>\n<table><thead><tr><th>Michoro</th><th>Rudisha</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>\"Hole-in-one!\"</td></tr><tr><td>&#x3C;= par - 2</td><td>\"Eagle\"</td></tr><tr><td>par - 1</td><td>\"Birdie\"</td></tr><tr><td>par</td><td>\"Par\"</td></tr><tr><td>par + 1</td><td>\"Bogey\"</td></tr><tr><td>par + 2</td><td>\"Double Bogey\"</td></tr><tr><td>>= par + 3</td><td>\"Go Home!\"</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><code>par</code> i <code>strokes</code> ce uvek biti pozitivni brojevi. Dodat je niz sa svim nazivima radi lakseg rada.</p>\n</section>","id":"5664820f61c48e80c9fa476c","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18195,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/golf-code"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"const names = [\"Hole-in-one!\", \"Eagle\", \"Birdie\", \"Par\", \"Bogey\", \"Double Bogey\", \"Go Home!\"];\n\nfunction golfScore(par, strokes) {\n  // Only change code below this line\n\n\n  return \"Change Me\";\n  // Only change code above this line\n}\n\ngolfScore(5, 4);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(4, 1)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Hole-in-one!</code></p>","testString":"assert(golfScore(4, 1) === 'Hole-in-one!');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(4, 2)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Eagle</code></p>","testString":"assert(golfScore(4, 2) === 'Eagle');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(5, 2)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Eagle</code></p>","testString":"assert(golfScore(5, 2) === 'Eagle');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(4, 3)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Birdie</code></p>","testString":"assert(golfScore(4, 3) === 'Birdie');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(4, 4)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Par</code></p>","testString":"assert(golfScore(4, 4) === 'Par');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(1, 1)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Hole-in-one!</code></p>","testString":"assert(golfScore(1, 1) === 'Hole-in-one!');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(5, 5)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Par</code></p>","testString":"assert(golfScore(5, 5) === 'Par');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(4, 5)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Bogey</code></p>","testString":"assert(golfScore(4, 5) === 'Bogey');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(4, 6)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Double Bogey</code></p>","testString":"assert(golfScore(4, 6) === 'Double Bogey');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(4, 7)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Go Home!</code></p>","testString":"assert(golfScore(4, 7) === 'Go Home!');"},{"text":"<p><code>golfScore(5, 9)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Go Home!</code></p>","testString":"assert(golfScore(5, 9) === 'Go Home!');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#basic-javascript","dashedName":"golf-code","ce